Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：spirit ZERO；校對：NT000A；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（早上啦  又是新一天的開始）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在平時  我會叫長門同學一塊起床的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天是週末  就讓她多睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:23.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（通宵了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我洗臉去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我一個人上不去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才踢那麼狠  她現在肯定起不來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  只能使用那招了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘技·彈牆跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉…水…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在拷問啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從提示的情報中選擇了你最容易吐槽的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:07.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（睡迷糊了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吐槽吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份怨念  一定要消除！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希  這裡這裡～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  竟然遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微昏迷了一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？沒事吧  難道有敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算不上敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  我很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  長門同學到阿虛那裡去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為激進派在這裡做這個怎麼行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這麼下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:01:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘真管用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼高也能夠得著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要有傘或許就無所不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小朝倉得意忘形了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯什麼的對現在的我來說絲毫不是障礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧  阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上消滅你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈…哈…哈……哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實小孩子一個人外出太危險了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（放棄了）

